# 4. 暗闇から、一歩

Ena: Ugh, it's so bright out...
Ena: *Sigh* It feels so weird being outside during the day like this.
Airi: Well, yeah, that'll happen when you're always cooped up indoors.
Ena: I know, but...
Airi: Yeah, I get it. But we're getting your feet back under you, so you'll just have to bear it.
Airi: Come on. Those pancakes won't eat themselves!
Ena: Yeah...
Waiter: Two orders of our heart-shaped fruit pancakes. They'll be out shortly.
Airi: Okay, thank you.
Airi: The pancakes here are really good. I'm sure you're gonna love them, Ena.
Ena: That's cool...
Ena: (Airi must be so busy with all her idol work... I really can't thank her enough for doing this.)
Ena: (If she didn't contact me that time, then I probably would've...)
Ena: Still no good...
Ena: (Why...?)
Ena: (Every time, I feel like I'm getting somewhere, and then it all just falls apart on me.)
Ena: (Am I just hopeless...?)
Ena: (No matter how much I draw...)
Ena: Hashtag...selfie... That's fine.
Ena: Hehe. Look at all these comments...
Ena: Everyone... They're praising me so much...
Ena: (Is this all there is for me?)
Ena: (Not being able to draw. Not acknowledged by anyone...)
Ena: (Do I really have to keep living on like this...?)
Ena: I want to disappear...
Ena: (I'm in a total daze...)
Ena: (I really haven't done much lately other than sleep and fiddle with my phone.)
Ena: (Turns out you don't really get hungry if you spend the whole day sleeping...)
Ena: (I bet my skin's a nightmare, but who cares? Even taking selfies is too much of a hassle.)
Ena: (Nothing matters now. I'm sick of everything...)
Ena: ...?
Ena: A song recommendation...?
Ena: Who posted this...? K...?
Ena: So this is what's popular lately?
Ena: It's so happy and cheerful...
Ena: Must be nice, having hope.
Ena: Huh...?
Ena: Airi...?
Airi: What's wrong, Ena?
Ena: Oh, umm...
Ena: Sorry, Airi.
Airi: Huh?
Ena: I know you're super busy... I feel really terrible about making you meet with me over and over again like this.
Airi: Don't say that...!
Airi: I wouldn't be much of an idol if I didn't take the time to help my best friend, would I?
Airi: I'm here because I want to be here! So... Ena, there's no need for you to apologize.
Ena: Airi...
Ena: Thanks...
